sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Siri
    participant GoogleAssistant
    participant System

    User->>Siri: "Hey Siri, set a reminder"
    Siri->>System: "Create reminder"
    System-->>Siri: "Reminder created"
    Siri-->>User: "Reminder set"

    User->>GoogleAssistant: "Ok Google, play music"
    GoogleAssistant->>System: "Play music command"
    System-->>GoogleAssistant: "Playing music"
    GoogleAssistant-->>User: "Now playing music"